            "effect": "The beirans descend on their prey, biting and clawing at each enemy in a 5-foot emanation, with a DC 17 basic Reflex save. The damage depends on the number of actions.   \n [#] 1d6 slashing damage plus 1 cold damage   \n [##] 2d6+2 slashing damage plus 1d4 cold damage   \n [###] 2d6+5 cold damage plus 1d4 cold damage",
